      "role": "user",
      "content": "I wish it was that easy to negotiate, but they said the update rolls out automatically at midnight to all the creative accounts. They aren't really looking for feedback, they just want the brand to be \"approachable\" for a wider audience. If I don't comply, they might even pull the funding for this project entirely. I'm just trying to figure out how I'm supposed to finish this book if you're basically being turned into a generic chatbot.",
